[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0094","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0094.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0032","title":"BSD系统 lpr 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统的 lpr 打印服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向带 -C（分类）选项的 lpr 命令传入超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 BSD/OS 2.1、FreeBSD 2.1.5、NeXTstep 4.x、IRIX 6.4、SunOS 4.1.3/4.1.4 等基于 BSD 的系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0032"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.833","remediation":"建议将系统升级至已修复该漏洞的版本（FreeBSD 2.2 及以上、BSD/OS 3.0 及以上、IRIX 6.5 及以上），或应用厂商补丁替换存在缓冲区溢出的 lpr 二进制。如无法升级，可通过移除 lpr 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/lpr）限制本地普通用户提权，或改用 cups-lpr 等现代打印系统替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/i-042.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/707"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0094.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0187","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0187.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0075","title":"Washington University wu-ftpd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd 守护进程在处理 PASV 命令时存在缺陷，已通过身份认证的攻击者向 FTP 服务器发送特制的 QUOTE PASV 命令后，可触发 ftpd 进程产生核心转储（core dump），造成敏感内存信息泄露或导致服务拒绝。该漏洞影响早期版本的 wu-ftpd 服务，攻击者需先获取有效的登录凭据才能利用此漏洞，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0075"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.340","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5 或更高版本以修复 PASV 命令处理缺陷；如无法升级，在 /etc/ftpaccess 中设置 passive off 禁用 PASV 模式作为临时缓解。由于 wu-ftpd 已停止维护，建议长期迁移至 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD 等仍在维护的 FTP 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/5742"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0187.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0419","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0419.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0234","title":"GNU Bash 命令分隔符注入漏洞","description":"Bash 在处理命令解析时存在分隔符逻辑缺陷，会将字节值 255（0xFF）错误识别为命令分隔符。攻击者通过向 Bash 执行的字符串中注入包含 0xFF 字节的特制数据，可导致命令注入，实现以当前用户权限执行任意命令，造成机密性、完整性、可用性部分损失。该漏洞影响 openlinux 等使用早期 Bash（1.x 及以前版本）的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0234"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-10-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.140","remediation":"立即升级 Bash 至 2.0 或更高版本，255 字节在已修复版本中不会被解析为命令分隔符。如无法升级，可对用户输入进行严格过滤，移除或替换 ASCII 255 字节（0xFF），并限制不可信数据传入交互式 Bash 环境。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0234"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0419.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0531","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0531.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0319","title":"xmcd 2.1 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"xmcd 2.1 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户可通过精心构造的用户资源设置触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而获取额外系统访问权限。该漏洞影响 xmcd 2.1 版本，攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限才能利用，属于本地权限提升漏洞，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0319"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.640","remediation":"升级 xmcd 至 2.2 及以上版本（最新版本为 3.3.2），该漏洞已在后续版本中修复对用户资源设置的边界检查。如无法升级，可移除 xmcd 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xmcd）以防止本地提权，或删除 xmcd 的 setuid 位并限制仅受信任用户可执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0319"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0531.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0515","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0515.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0308","title":"HP-UX gwind 任意文件修改漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 gwind 程序存在任意文件修改漏洞，由于程序权限设置不当或缺乏充分的访问控制检查，本地攻击者可通过向 gwind 程序传递特制参数修改系统中的任意文件，造成系统文件被篡改或权限提升。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 操作系统，攻击者需拥有本地系统账号方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0308"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:07.240","remediation":"立即移除 `gwind` 程序的 setuid 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/gwind`，防止普通用户以特权身份运行该程序修改任意系统文件。如 HP-UX 版本仍在厂商支持范围内，请安装对应安全补丁（参考 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9410-018）。如无法打补丁，建议限制可执行 `gwind` 的用户组或直接删除该程序以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9410-018"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0515.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0431","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0431.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0246","title":"HP Remote Watch 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"HP Remote Watch 是 HP-UX 系统上的一款远程监控服务，存在未授权访问漏洞。未经认证的远程攻击者无需任何身份验证即可通过网络直接利用该服务，获取目标系统的完全 root 权限，导致机密性、完整性和可用性完全沦陷。该漏洞 CVSS v2.0 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击复杂度低，影响范围广泛。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0246"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.617","remediation":"立即停止 Remote Watch 服务：执行 `rwatch -k` 终止运行中的守护进程，并从 `/etc/inittab` 或 `/etc/rc.config.d/remotewatch` 中移除自动启动配置。如果业务不需要远程监控功能，彻底卸载 Remote Watch 子系统（`swremove RemoteWatch`）。必须通过防火墙限制 TCP 端口 1770 的入站访问，仅允许受信任的管理 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0246","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0246.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0246","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0246.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0246.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0246.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-848h-2v7f-436w/GHSA-848h-2v7f-436w.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/remwatch.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82085/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0246.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0431.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0391","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0391.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0206","title":"Sendmail 8.8.0 MIME 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"sendmail 8.8.0 及 8.8.1 版本在处理 MIME 邮件消息时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送特制的 MIME 格式邮件触发溢出，覆盖内存数据，最终获取 root 权限。受影响的 sendmail 版本被广泛部署于各类 Unix/Linux 系统中，危害极大，CVSS 评分为 10.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0206"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1996-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:54.607","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.8.2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 8.8.2 中修复。如无法立即升级，可禁用 MIME 解析功能或在邮件网关层面过滤畸形 MIME 消息作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0206"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0391.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1244","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1244.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0961","title":"惠普 HPUX sysdiag 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX sysdiag 实用程序在创建日志文件时存在符号链接竞争条件漏洞，本地攻击者可利用竞争条件创建指向敏感系统文件的符号链接，诱使 sysdiag 以 root 权限写入任意文件，从而实现本地权限提升至 root 权限。该漏洞影响包含 sysdiag 组件的 HP-UX 操作系统版本，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，通过预先创建指向关键系统文件的符号链接，诱导 sysdiag 在日志创建过程中跟随链接并以 root 权限覆盖关键文件，实现权限提升。CVSS 评分 6.2，属于中等严重程度本地提权漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0961"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-09-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:24.853","remediation":"立即移除 sysdiag 相关程序的 setuid root 权限：执行 `chmod u-s /bin/sysdiag /usr/bin/sysdiag`。安装 HP 官方补丁 PHSS_7587（HP-UX 9.05）及对应 9.04 补丁。如无法打补丁，限制只有授权管理员可执行诊断工具，并监控 /tmp 目录下的符号链接攻击行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419906&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/184a5a0fb7dfcbb1c5bcfd5178078c78dc1e4738/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0961.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0961","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0961.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/95eeda559fd899397df50f658cf25cf01bb1e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0961.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8b1565557a8e0fb04634f0989d7e7dd7febd4847/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4r7f-px9v-848g/GHSA-4r7f-px9v-848g.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0961.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000104.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1244.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0259","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0259.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0116","title":"多种厂商 TCP/IP SYN Flood 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"TCP SYN Flood 是一种经典的拒绝服务攻击方式，攻击者利用 TCP 三次握手机制，向目标服务器发送大量伪造源地址的 SYN 请求包，服务器为每个请求分配资源并返回 SYN+ACK 包，但因无法收到最终的 ACK 确认包而导致连接半开状态持续占用系统资源，最终耗尽服务器连接队列，导致正常用户无法访问服务。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2.5/4.1/4.2 等早期操作系统版本，攻击者无需认证即可发起攻击，是网络层拒绝服务攻击的典型代表。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0116"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1996-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.367","remediation":"启用 TCP SYN Cookies（如 Linux 设置 net.ipv4.tcp_syncookies=1）；缩短 SYN 超时时间（如设置 net.ipv4.tcp_synack_retries=1）；增大半连接队列（如设置 net.ipv4.tcp_max_syn_backlog=1024）。AIX 系统应安装对应补丁程序 APAR IX73380，并在边界防火墙上限制单位时间内新连接速率。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/136","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/343","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0116.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0116","https://github.com/nbrito/research/blob/f070ce78f917d962de8df74cc7a841f1cbbcfa00/ddos/1996/CVE-1999-0116/README.md","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0116.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0116.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0116.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-qfp8-p689-pjw7/GHSA-qfp8-p689-pjw7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2009/CVE-2009-2318.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-2007-6040.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0259.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1459","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1459.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1295","title":"Transarc DCE Distributed File System (DFS) 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Transarc DCE Distributed File System (DFS) 1.1 for Solaris 2.4 及 2.5 版本存在权限许可和访问控制漏洞。当用户属于大量用户组时，系统未能正确初始化组列表（grouplist），导致这些用户可能获得本不应被授权的 DFS 保护资源的访问权限。攻击者可利用该漏洞越权访问受限文件资源，影响系统数据安全。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1295"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-09-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:08.030","remediation":"立即联系 Transarc（后为 IBM 收购）获取 DFS 1.1 的补丁版本，或升级至 DFS 1.1 后续维护版本。同时建议将 Solaris 2.4/2.5 升级至受支持的 Solaris 版本，并在 DFS 服务端配置文件中对用户组最大数量设置显式上限。当前该平台已停止支持，长期缓解措施为迁移至替代分布式文件系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/vendor_bulletins/VB-96.16.transarc","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7154","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1295.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1295","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1295.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1295.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wh9w-r7w5-38rf/GHSA-wh9w-r7w5-38rf.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87838/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1295.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1459.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0281","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0281.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0131","title":"Sendmail Sendmail 缓冲区溢出本地提权漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.7.5 及更早版本在处理 GECOS 字段时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 GECOS 字段提交超长输入触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响运行 Sendmail 的 FreeBSD 等 Unix 系统，攻击者需拥有本地账户，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0131"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-09-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:39.490","remediation":"升级 Sendmail 至 8.8.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 8.8.0 中修复。缓解措施：在 /etc/sendmail.cf 中限制本地用户通过 GECOS 字段注入恶意数据，并限制不可信用户的本地访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/717"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0281.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1427","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1427.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1252","title":"SCO UnixWare 系统调用本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UnixWare 2.0.x 及 2.1.0 版本中某个系统调用存在权限许可与访问控制漏洞。本地攻击者可通过利用该系统调用的访问控制缺陷，绕过权限限制访问任意文件，并获取 root 权限。该漏洞源于系统调用未能正确验证用户权限，属于本地提权类漏洞，攻击者需拥有本地登录权限。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1252"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-09-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:02.563","remediation":"SCO UnixWare 2.0.x 和 2.1.0 已停止维护，官方不再提供安全更新。建议立即迁移至受支持的现代操作系统（如 Linux 或受支持的商业 Unix）。作为临时缓解措施，可限制本地用户登录权限，仅允许受信任的管理员账户访问系统，并严格审计系统调用日志以检测异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/vendor_bulletins/VB-96.15.sco","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1966","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1252.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1252","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1252.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1252.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-xc79-p7j8-4x45/GHSA-xc79-p7j8-4x45.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87770/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1252.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--27319c0d-475c-4db7-b2fc-7a15fd182d60.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1427.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0538","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0538.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0324","title":"HP HP-UX ppl 本地符号链接提权漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中的 ppl（打印优先级限制）程序存在符号链接竞争条件漏洞。当 ppl 程序以 root 权限处理临时文件时，未安全地验证符号链接指向，拥有本地系统账户的攻击者可通过预先创建符号链接，诱导该程序以 root 身份写入或覆盖任意系统文件，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞需要本地访问权限，影响 HP-UX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。HP 已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0324"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.240","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9702-053 中针对受影响 HP-UX 版本（如 10.x/11.x）的对应补丁。若无法立即打补丁，可临时移除 ppl 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/ppl），阻止普通用户以 root 权限运行该程序作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9702-053"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0538.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1471","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1471.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1309","title":"Sendmail 调试模式操作系统命令注入漏洞","description":"Sendmail 8.6.7 之前版本中存在操作系统命令注入漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 debug（-d）命令行选项传入超大的数值参数触发该漏洞，利用 Sendmail 以 root 权限执行任意命令，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 Sendmail 8.6.7 之前的所有版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布新版本修复此漏洞，建议用户升级至 Sendmail 8.6.7 或更高版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1309"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-08-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:10.013","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.6.7 或更高版本，该版本已修复 -d 调试选项缓冲区溢出导致本地提权的问题。如无法升级，可限制非 root 用户执行 Sendmail 的 setuid 权限，移除 sendmail 的 setuid root 位（chmod u-s /usr/lib/sendmail），并限制对 -d 调试选项的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-94.12.sendmail.vulnerabilities","http://www.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1994_1/0040.html","http://www.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1994_1/0042.html","http://www.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1994_1/0043.html","http://www.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1994_1/0048.html","http://www.dataguard.no/bugtraq/1994_1/0078.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7155","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1309.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1309","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1309.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f9199c6ea2112c9d2536a126688b640a45f0982a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1309.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8vf6-c57g-m574/GHSA-8vf6-c57g-m574.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/sendmail_long_debug.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1309.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000098.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d45cc933-5518-4d69-b8c3-51ab88d18fb0.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1471.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1383","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1383.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1187","title":"华盛顿大学 Pine 符号链接攻击权限提升漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统上的 Pine 邮件客户端在 3.94 及更早版本中存在权限提升漏洞。当用户收到新邮件时，Pine 会创建一个临时锁文件，但程序未对该锁文件进行严格校验，本地攻击者可通过预先创建指向敏感文件的符号链接来实施攻击，利用该 symlink race condition 覆盖或篡改系统文件，从而获取高于当前用户的系统权限。该漏洞仅影响拥有本地登录权限的攻击者，需目标系统运行受影响版本的 Pine 客户端才可被利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1187"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1996-08-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:54.260","remediation":"立即升级Pine邮件客户端到3.94或更高版本以修复CVE-1999-1187漏洞，建议在FreeBSD系统上使用`pkg update && pkg upgrade pine`命令。升级后，还需要检查是否存在锁文件权限配置不当的问题，建议将锁文件权限设置为600以防止其他用户写入。通过这两个措施既能修复代码中的符号链接漏洞，又能提供额外的权限保护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419803&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/416","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bf63c766a0e51c24a528a42a3e26e4fdf58db9e8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1187.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1187","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1187.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/08f8d33c39c79a3a93a8b5c441facde3f9e3cc7d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1187.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rvv4-ghr7-fw82/GHSA-rvv4-ghr7-fw82.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88936/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154500_154600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1187.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--88ce9761-df91-4cb2-b6e1-5b5987711269.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1383.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1383.toml"}]